title: [Niadja's Magic Shoppe]
[Niadja's Outfitting]
description: A tropical bloom wreath hangs on one of the dark oak walls, and an oak-framed ceiling rises overhead.  A well-pruned lemon tree sits in one corner of a russet oak floor.  There is a vine-carved mahogany table on one side of the shop and a floral-etched ceramic case on the other.
